data.description: This spacious and affordable 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home situated on a double lot is located a stone's throw from the river and is ready for it's new owners! Located in Titusville, FL close to Kennedy Space Center and Space X this is the perfect location for all space enthusiasts. The huge lot and metal outbuilding provide plenty of space to store all of your toys Among the lush, tropical landscaping. This concrete block home features a brand new roof, hurricane rated windows, new electrical panel, workshop, and a fenced in yard. The interior features tile floor and an open floor plan showcasing a kitchen peninsula and newer appliances with built in oven. You can walk out to your huge screened in porch, perfect for relaxing and enjoying a cup of coffee in the morning. Don't wait long - this perfect home in an established neighborhood won't last. All information deemed accurate but to be verified by buyers and buyers agent. ;Water: City
